works.description: Roja Dove, master perfumer of Harrods Haute Parfumerie, was lately reported to have commissioned the famous perfumer Clive Christian to create special perfume bottles for the Royal couple. Pictured above are the custom Clive Christian No. 1 Pure Perfumes made especially for Prince William and Catherine Middleton on behalf of Roja Dove Haute Parfumerie and Clive Christian Perfumes.
